msgctxt "mn120:37.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu saddhāya samannāgato hoti, sīlena …"
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, take a mendicant who has faith, ethics, learning, generosity, "
"and wisdom."

msgctxt "mn120:37.2"
msgid "sutena …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn120:37.3"
msgid "cāgena …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn120:37.4"
msgid "paññāya samannāgato hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn120:37.5"
msgid "Tassa evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "They think:"

msgctxt "mn120:37.6"
msgid ""
"‘aho vatāhaṃ āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva "
"dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja vihareyyan’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘If only I might realize the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by "
"wisdom in this very life, and live having realized it with my own insight "
"due to the ending of defilements.’"

msgctxt "mn120:37.7"
msgid ""
"So āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ "
"abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"They realize the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in this "
"very life. And they live having realized it with their own insight due to "
"the ending of defilements."

#. VAR: na katthaci upapajjatī”ti → na kuhiñci upapajjatīti (bj) | na katthaci uppajjati na kuhiñci uppajjatīti (pts1) | na kuhiñci upasampajja viharatīti. (mr)
msgctxt "mn120:37.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na katthaci upapajjatī”ti."
msgstr "And, mendicants, that mendicant is not reborn anywhere.”"

